@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ohkiwi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.14
    v1 = v0
    v2 = 0.52
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.exp((tmp + 0.27 / tmp + 0.78)))
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.exp(v0 + 0.90) - v0))
    tmp = (((v2 + 0.92 * v1 + 0.81) - (v1 + 0.91 + v2 + 0.35)) - wp.exp((v0 + 0.70 + v2 + 0.59)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(0.04))
    data[tid] = v0
